title: I Soliti Ignoti (1958) (CC)
description:
Mario Monicelli's classic crime comedy I Soliti Ignoti features Vittorio Gassman and Marcello Mastroianni as a pair of thieves who head a group of criminals in a break-in attempt. Their plan involves digging an underground tunnel from an apartment that leads to a neighboring business and drilling their way inside. In addition to each of the burglars struggling with individual personal problems.
